  "name": "Steel Wind Strike",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You flourish the weapon used in the casting and then vanish to strike like the wind. Choose up to five creatures you can see within range. Make a melee spell attack against each target. On a hit, a target takes [[/r 6d10]] force damage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>You can then teleport to an unoccupied space you can see within 5 feet of one of the targets you hit or missed.</p></div>",
